Mr. Lawrence https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mr._Lawrence 0 Douglas Lawrence Osowski credited as Mr. Lawrence and sometimes Doug Lawrence, is an American animator, writer, and voice actor. He is noted for his work as a writer and occasional voice actor for the Nicktoons Rocko's Modern Life and SpongeBob SquarePants.
